## Insurance and Liability Considerations

Event planning involves understanding liability and insurance coverage because corporate transportation affects company responsibility for employee and client safety. Limousine services operate under different regulatory and insurance frameworks than other transportation options.

According to [Colorado Department of Transportation](https://www.codot.gov/) regulations, commercial limousine services must maintain specific insurance coverage levels and undergo regular vehicle inspections. These requirements create safety and reliability standards that support business travel needs.

